# 🧪 Learning Takeaways

* Modular architecture with cogs
* JSON-based persistence
* Event-driven design
* Shared-state systems
* UI interaction patterns

---

# ⚠️ Design Tradeoffs

* Heavy JSON usage
* Shared file risks
* Repeated permission logic
* Cross-cog coupling

